flowchart TD
    A[Session state change] --> B{State}

    B -->|PRE_CASTING| C[ApplySessionState calls FadeOutUI]
    B -->|CLOSING_FISHING_SESSION| D[ApplySessionState calls RestoreFocusVisualsAfterLinger]
    B -->|CANCELLING_FISHING_SESSION| E[ApplySessionState calls ForceVisibleFocusVisuals]
    B -->|Other states| F[No direct state-triggered fade call]

    C --> G{FadeOutUI guard\nisFading?}
    G -->|yes| H[Ignore request]
    G -->|no| I[Set isFading=true, clear restoreAt]

    I --> J[Per frame: read current shown+alpha]
    J --> K{Capture baseline?\nnot isFaded and not IsFrameFading and not IsBaselineCaptureSuppressed}
    K -->|yes| L[Cache wasShownByName + originalAlphaByName]
    K -->|no| M[Keep existing baseline]

    L --> N[Remove pending frame fade timer]
    M --> N
    N --> O{shown and alpha > 0.001}
    O -->|yes| P[Disable clicks and FadeOut to 0.0001 over 3.0s]
    O -->|no| Q[Skip frame fade]

    P --> R["Hide supporting UI groups\n(minimap/buttons/micro menu/elv helpers)"]
    Q --> R
    R --> S[Set isFaded=true, isFading=false]

    D --> T{RestoreFocusVisualsAfterLinger guard}
    T -->|not faded| U[No-op]
    T -->|feature disabled| V[FadeInUI immediately]
    T -->|linger <= 0 or no GetTime| V
    T -->|linger > 0| W[Set restoreAt = now + linger]

    W --> X[Focus frame OnUpdate]
    X --> Y{now >= restoreAt}
    Y -->|no| X
    Y -->|yes| V

    V --> ZA{FadeInUI guard\nisFading?}
    ZA -->|yes| ZB[Ignore request]
    ZA -->|no| ZC[Set isFading=true]

    ZC --> ZD["Set cacheSuppressUntil = now + 3.0s"]
    ZD --> ZE["Per frame FadeFrameIn(3.0)"]
    ZE --> ZF{wasShown baseline?\nif nil fallback to frame:IsShown}
    ZF -->|true| ZG[Enable clicks, clear alpha override, remove fade timer, show frame]
    ZF -->|false| ZH[Leave hidden]

    ZG --> ZI[Target alpha = originalAlpha,\nfall back to 1.0 if nil/<=threshold]
    ZI --> ZJ[FadeIn to target over 3.0s]

    ZJ --> ZK["Restore supporting UI groups\n(minimap/buttons/micro menu/elv helpers)"]
    ZH --> ZK
    ZK --> ZL[Copy restoreExpected* from baseline cache]
    ZL --> ZM[Clear baseline caches, set isFaded=false, restoreAt=nil, isFading=false]

    E --> ZN[ForceVisibleFocusVisuals]
    ZN --> ZO["Set isFading=true, clear restoreAt/cacheSuppressUntil"]
    ZO --> ZP["Per frame FadeFrameIn(0.0)\n(immediate for previously visible frames)"]
    ZP --> ZQ["Restore supporting UI groups\n(minimap/buttons/micro menu/elv helpers), set isFaded=false, isFading=false"]

    F --> ZR[RefreshFocusFadeState path]
    ZR --> ZS{PRE_CASTING?}
    ZS -->|yes and not isFaded| C
    ZS -->|yes and restoreAt set| ZT[Clear pending restoreAt]
    ZS -->|no| ZU{isFishingSessionActive and restoreAt set}
    ZU -->|yes| ZV[Clear pending restoreAt]
    ZU -->|no| ZW{close/cancel state and isFaded}
    ZW -->|yes| D
    ZW -->|no and not fishing and isFaded| V
